---
title: Haloumi & Currant Couscous with Roasted Veggies & Lemon Yoghurt
description: Taste the rainbow for dinner tonight with an assortment of colourful roasted veggies and a scattering of currants, all stirred through fluffy,
filling couscous. Topped off with golden haloumi and this robust dinner packs a punch in all the right ways.

*Keep an eye out...
Due to recent sourcing
challenges, we’ve replaced
pumpkin with potato, which
may be a little different to
what’s pictured. Don’t worry,
your recipe will be just as
delicious!*
